cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with generating 3D shapes from natural language descriptions, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves learning embeddings and making use of machine learning techniques such as GANs, which fall under the sub-categories of cs.LG, cs.AI. Finally, the paper deals with 3D shapes, which falls under the sub-category of cs.GR.
